  "keyFeatures": [
    "Python SDK with NumPy interoperability and GPU-accelerated image processing",
    "C++ SDK for production medical imaging applications",
    "Plugin-based architecture with 15+ domain modules (Ultrasound, CT, Spine, Navigation, etc.)",
    "ImFusion Suite — visual GUI for algorithm prototyping with Python REPL",
    "ImFusion Labels — AI training data annotation with smart segmentation tools",
    "Built-in ML pipeline support with model inference, datasets, and preprocessing operations",
    "Ask AI documentation assistant for instant answers",
    "MCP Server for connecting ImFusion SDK tools to AI coding assistants",
    "DICOM, NIfTI, MHD, HDF5, and custom format support",
    "Cross-platform: Windows, Linux, macOS",
    "ISO 13485 certified with regulatory compliance support"
